Require Import List Streams Nat Bool.
Import ListNotations.
Require Import Lia.
Require Import Logic.FunctionalExtensionality.

Require Import Coq.Logic.FinFun Coq.Logic.Eqdep.

From CasperCBC
Require Import Lib.StreamExtras Lib.ListExtras Lib.Preamble VLSM.Common VLSM.Composition.

Section ProjectionTraces.

Context
  {message : Type}
  {index : Type}
  {IndEqDec : EqDecision index}
  (IM : index -> VLSM message)
  {i0 : Inhabited index}
  (constraint : composite_label IM -> composite_state IM * option message -> Prop)
  (X := composite_vlsm IM constraint)
  (j : index)
  (Xj := composite_vlsm_constrained_projection IM constraint j)
  .

Fixpoint finite_trace_projection_list
  (trx : list (vtransition_item X))
  : list (vtransition_item Xj)
  :=
  match trx with
  | [] => []
  | item :: trx =>
    let tail := finite_trace_projection_list trx in
    let s := destination item in
    let l := l item in
    let x := projT1 l in
    match decide (j = x) with
    | left e =>
      let lj := eq_rect_r _ (projT2 l) e in
      @Build_transition_item _ (type Xj) lj (input item) (s j) (output item) :: tail
    | _ => tail
    end
  end.

Definition from_projection
  (a : vtransition_item X)
  : Prop
  := j = projT1 (l a).

Instance dec_from_projection (a : transition_item) : Decision (from_projection a) :=
  decide (from_projection a).

Definition finite_trace_projection_list_alt
  (trx : list (vtransition_item X))
  (ftrx := (filter (fun a => bool_decide (from_projection a)) trx))
  (Hall: Forall from_projection ftrx)
  :=
  List.map
    (fun item : {a : vtransition_item X | from_projection a} =>
      let (item, e) := item in
      let lj := eq_rect_r _ (projT2 (l item)) e in
      @Build_transition_item _ (type Xj)
        lj
        (input item)
        (destination item j)
        (output item)
    )
  (list_annotate from_projection ftrx Hall).

finite_trace_projection_list_alt (a :: trx) Hall =
match decide (j = projT1 (l a)) with
| left e =>
    {|
    l := eq_rect_r (fun n : index => vlabel (IM n))
           (projT2 (l a)) e;
    input := input a;
    destination := destination a j;
    output := output a |}
    :: finite_trace_projection_list trx
| right _ => finite_trace_projection_list trx
end

i0:Inhabited index
constraint:composite_label IM ->

Prop
X:=composite_vlsm IM constraint:VLSM message

  constraint j:VLSM message
a:vtransition_item X

IHtr1:finite_trace_projection_list (tr1 ++ tr2) =
finite_trace_projection_list tr1 ++
finite_trace_projection_list tr2
finite_trace_projection_list ((a :: tr1) ++ tr2) =
finite_trace_projection_list (a :: tr1) ++
finite_trace_projection_list tr2

  
message, index:Type
IndEqDec:EqDecision index
IM:index -> VLSM message
i0:Inhabited index
constraint:composite_label IM ->
composite_state IM * option message ->
Prop
X:=composite_vlsm IM constraint:VLSM message
j:index
Xj:=composite_vlsm_constrained_projection IM
  constraint j:VLSM message
a:vtransition_item X
tr1, tr2:list (vtransition_item X)
IHtr1:finite_trace_projection_list (tr1 ++ tr2) =
finite_trace_projection_list tr1 ++
finite_trace_projection_list tr2
match decide (j = projT1 (l a)) with
| left e =>
    {|
    l := eq_rect_r (fun n : index => vlabel (IM n))
           (projT2 (l a)) e;
    input := input a;
    destination := destination a j;
    output := output a |}
    :: finite_trace_projection_list (tr1 ++ tr2)
| right _ => finite_trace_projection_list (tr1 ++ tr2)
end =
match decide (j = projT1 (l a)) with
| left e =>
    {|
    l := eq_rect_r (fun n : index => vlabel (IM n))
           (projT2 (l a)) e;
    input := input a;
    destination := destination a j;
    output := output a |}
    :: finite_trace_projection_list tr1
| right _ => finite_trace_projection_list tr1
end ++ finite_trace_projection_list tr2

message, index:Type
IndEqDec:EqDecision index
IM:index -> VLSM message
i0:Inhabited index
constraint:composite_label IM ->
composite_state IM * option message ->
Prop
X:=composite_vlsm IM constraint:VLSM message
j:index
Xj:=composite_vlsm_constrained_projection IM
  constraint j:VLSM message
s:state
tl:list transition_item
Htr:finite_protocol_trace_from
  (pre_loaded_with_all_messages_vlsm X) s tl
s':state
iom, oom:option message
l:label
H:protocol_transition
  (pre_loaded_with_all_messages_vlsm X) l
  (s', iom) (s, oom)
IHHtr:last
  (List.map destination
     (finite_trace_projection_list tl)) 
  (s j) = last (List.map destination tl) s j
last
  (List.map destination
     (finite_trace_projection_list
        ({|
         l := l;
         input := iom;
         destination := s;
         output := oom |} :: tl))) (s' j) =
last
  (List.map destination
     ({|
      l := l;
      input := iom;
      destination := s;
      output := oom |} :: tl)) s' j

IM:index -> VLSM message
i0:Inhabited index
constraint:composite_label IM ->
composite_state IM * option message ->
Prop
X:=composite_vlsm IM constraint:VLSM message

Xj:=composite_vlsm_constrained_projection IM
  constraint j:VLSM message

transitions:list (vtransition_item X)
Htr:finite_protocol_trace_from X start transitions
lstx:=last (List.map destination transitions) start:state
lstj:=last
  (List.map destination
     (finite_trace_projection_list transitions))
  (start j):state
lstj = lstx j

  (existT (fun n : index => vlabel (IM n)) x lx)

IHHtr:protocol_state_prop Xj (s j) ->
finite_protocol_trace_from Xj 
  (s j) (finite_trace_projection_list tl)
finite_protocol_trace_from Xj (s' j)
  match decide (j = x) with
  | left e =>
      {|
      l := eq_rect_r (fun n : index => vlabel (IM n))
             lx e;
      input := iom;
      destination := s j;
      output := oom |}
      :: finite_trace_projection_list tl
  | right _ => finite_trace_projection_list tl
  end

finite_protocol_trace_from Xj si'
  (finite_trace_projection_list tl)
sj:state
HPjiom:protocol_prop
  (composite_vlsm_constrained_projection IM
     constraint j) (sj, iom)
exists s : vstate (composite_vlsm IM constraint),
  s j = s' j /\
  protocol_state_prop (composite_vlsm IM constraint) s /\
  option_protocol_message_prop
    (composite_vlsm IM constraint) iom /\
  constrained_composite_valid IM constraint
    (existT (fun n : index => vlabel (IM n)) j lx)
    (s, iom)

  (s', iom)

Hps:protocol_state_prop X (state_update IM s' x s0)
Hpp:protocol_prop X (state_update IM s' x s0, oom)
IHHtr:protocol_state_prop Xj (s' j) ->
finite_protocol_trace_from Xj 
  (s' j) (finite_trace_projection_list tl)
Ht:(state_update IM s' x s0, oom) =
(state_update IM s' x s0, oom)
n:j <> x
protocol_state_prop Xj (s' j)

      assumption.
Qed.

(* The projection of a preloaded finite protocol trace remains a preloaded protocol trace *)

message, index:Type
IndEqDec:EqDecision index
IM:index -> VLSM message
i0:Inhabited index
constraint:composite_label IM ->
composite_state IM * option message ->
Prop
X:=composite_vlsm IM constraint:VLSM message
j:index
Xj:=composite_vlsm_constrained_projection IM
  constraint j:VLSM message
s':state
Psj:protocol_state_prop
  (pre_loaded_with_all_messages_vlsm (IM j))
  (s' j)
s:state
tl:list transition_item
Htr:finite_protocol_trace_from
  (pre_loaded_with_all_messages_vlsm X) s tl
iom, oom:option message
x:index
lx:vlabel (IM x)
H:protocol_transition
  (pre_loaded_with_all_messages_vlsm X)
  (existT (fun n : index => vlabel (IM n)) x lx)
  (s', iom) (s, oom)
IHHtr:protocol_state_prop
  (pre_loaded_with_all_messages_vlsm (IM j))
  (s j) ->
finite_protocol_trace_from
  (pre_loaded_with_all_messages_vlsm (IM j))
  (s j) (finite_trace_projection_list tl)
finite_protocol_trace_from
  (pre_loaded_with_all_messages_vlsm (IM j)) (s' j)
  match decide (j = x) with
  | left e =>
      {|
      l := eq_rect_r (fun n : index => vlabel (IM n))
             lx e;
      input := iom;
      destination := s j;
      output := oom |}
      :: finite_trace_projection_list tl
  | right _ => finite_trace_projection_list tl
  end

  (pre_loaded_with_all_messages_vlsm X) s'
Piom:option_protocol_message_prop
  (pre_loaded_with_all_messages_vlsm X) iom
Hv:free_composite_valid IM
  (existT (fun n : index => vlabel (IM n)) x lx)
  (s', iom)
Hc:constraint
  (existT (fun n : index => vlabel (IM n)) x lx)
  (s', iom)
Ht:transition
  (existT (fun n : index => vlabel (IM n)) x lx)
  (s', iom) = (s, oom)
IHHtr:protocol_state_prop
  (pre_loaded_with_all_messages_vlsm (IM j))
  (s j) ->

  (pre_loaded_with_all_messages_vlsm (IM j))
  (s j) (finite_trace_projection_list tl)
Hpp:protocol_prop
  (pre_loaded_with_all_messages_vlsm X) 
  (s, oom)
Hps:protocol_state_prop
  (pre_loaded_with_all_messages_vlsm X) s
finite_protocol_trace_from
  (pre_loaded_with_all_messages_vlsm (IM j)) (s' j)
  match decide (j = x) with
  | left e =>
      {|
      l := eq_rect_r (fun n : index => vlabel (IM n))
             lx e;
      input := iom;
      destination := s j;
      output := oom |}
      :: finite_trace_projection_list tl
  | right _ => finite_trace_projection_list tl
  end

  (state_update IM s' x s0, oom)

  (s1 j) (finite_trace_projection_list tr)
finite_protocol_trace_from X s1 tr

  assumption.

Definition in_projection
   (tr : Stream (vtransition_item X))
   (n : nat)
   := from_projection (Str_nth n tr).

Definition in_projection_dec
  := forall (tr : Stream (vtransition_item X)),
       bounding (in_projection tr)
       + { ss : monotone_nat_stream
         | filtering_subsequence from_projection tr ss
         }.

Definition infinite_trace_projection_stream
  (ss: Stream (vtransition_item X))
  (ks: monotone_nat_stream)
  (Hfilter: filtering_subsequence from_projection ss ks)
  : Stream (vtransition_item (IM j))
  :=
  let subs := stream_subsequence ss ks in
  let HForAll := stream_filter_Forall from_projection ss ks Hfilter in
  let subsP := stream_annotate from_projection subs HForAll in
  Streams.map
    (fun item : {a : vtransition_item X | from_projection a} =>
      let (item, e) := item in
      let lj := eq_rect_r _ (projT2 (l item)) e in
      @Build_transition_item _ (type Xj) lj (input item) (destination item j) (output item)
    )
    subsP.


message, index:Type
IndEqDec:EqDecision index
IM:index -> VLSM message
i0:Inhabited index
constraint:composite_label IM ->
composite_state IM * option message ->
Prop
X:=composite_vlsm IM constraint:VLSM message
j:index
Xj:=composite_vlsm_constrained_projection IM
  constraint j:VLSM message
ss:Stream (vtransition_item X)
ks:monotone_nat_stream
Hfilter:filtering_subsequence from_projection ss ks
n:nat
kn:=Str_nth n (proj1_sig ks):nat
ss_to_kn:=stream_prefix ss (succ kn):list (vtransition_item X)
sproj:=infinite_trace_projection_stream ss ks Hfilter:Stream (vtransition_item (IM j))
stream_prefix sproj (succ n) =
finite_trace_projection_list ss_to_kn

ss:Stream (vtransition_item X)
ks:monotone_nat_stream
Hfilter:filtering_subsequence from_projection ss ks
n:nat
kn:=Str_nth n (proj1_sig ks):nat
Hsfilter:stream_prefix (stream_subsequence ss ks)
  (S n) =
filter
  (fun a : vtransition_item X =>
   bool_decide (from_projection a))
  (stream_prefix ss
     (S (Str_nth n (proj1_sig ks))))
ss_to_kn:=stream_prefix ss (S kn):list (vtransition_item X)
Hall:Forall from_projection
  (filter
     (fun a : vtransition_item X =>
      bool_decide (from_projection a))
     (stream_prefix ss
        (S (Str_nth n (proj1_sig ks)))))
Heq:stream_prefix
  (stream_annotate from_projection
     (stream_subsequence ss ks)
     (stream_filter_Forall from_projection ss ks
        Hfilter)) (S n) =
list_annotate from_projection
  (filter
     (fun a : vtransition_item X =>
      bool_decide (from_projection a))
     (stream_prefix ss
        (S (Str_nth n (proj1_sig ks))))) Hall
List.map
  (fun
     item : {a : vtransition_item X
            | from_projection a} =>
   let (item0, e) := item in
   {|
   l := eq_rect_r (fun n : index => vlabel (IM n))
          (projT2 (l item0)) e;
   input := input item0;
   destination := destination item0 j;
   output := output item0 |})
  (list_annotate from_projection
     (filter
        (fun a : vtransition_item X =>
         bool_decide (from_projection a))
        (stream_prefix ss
           (S (Str_nth n (proj1_sig ks))))) Hall) =
finite_trace_projection_list
  (stream_prefix ss (S (Str_nth n (proj1_sig ks))))

  apply finite_trace_projection_list_alt_iff.
Qed.

Psj:protocol_state_prop Xj
  (trace_first (Infinite s ss) j)
Htr:ptrace_from_prop X (Infinite s ss)
n:nat
ptrace_from_prop Xj
  (Finite (s j)
     (finite_trace_projection_list
        (stream_prefix ss n)))

(* We axiomatize projection friendliness as the converse of protocol_trace_projection *)
Definition finite_projection_friendly
  := forall
    (sj : vstate (IM j))
    (trj : list (vtransition_item (IM j)))
    (Htrj : finite_protocol_trace Xj sj trj),
    exists (sx : vstate X) (trx : list (vtransition_item X)),
      finite_protocol_trace X sx trx
      /\ sx j = sj
      /\ finite_trace_projection_list trx = trj.

Definition projection_friendly
  (Hproj_dec : in_projection_dec)
  := forall
  (trj : vTrace (IM j))
  (Htrj : protocol_trace_prop Xj trj),
  exists (tr : vTrace X),
    protocol_trace_prop X tr
    /\ trace_projection Hproj_dec tr = trj.


message, index:Type
IndEqDec:EqDecision index
IM:index -> VLSM message
i0:Inhabited index
constraint:composite_label IM ->
composite_state IM * option message ->
Prop
X:=composite_vlsm IM constraint:VLSM message
j:index
Xj:=composite_vlsm_constrained_projection IM
  constraint j:VLSM message
Hproj_dec:in_projection_dec
Hfr:projection_friendly Hproj_dec
finite_projection_friendly

Htr:protocol_trace_prop X (Infinite s tr)
Heq:match Hproj_dec tr with
| inl (exist _ n1 _) =>
    Finite (s j)
      (finite_trace_projection_list
         (stream_prefix tr n1))
| inr (exist _ ks Hfilter) =>
    Infinite (s j)
      (infinite_trace_projection_stream tr ks
         Hfilter)
end = Finite sj trj
Htrj:finite_protocol_trace Xj sj trj
exists
  (sx : vstate X) (trx : list (vtransition_item X)),
  finite_protocol_trace X sx trx /\
  sx j = sj /\ finite_trace_projection_list trx = trj

     (List.map
        (fun
           item : {a : 
                  vtransition_item X
                  | from_projection a} =>
         let (item0, e) := item in
         {|
         l := eq_rect_r
                (fun n : index => vlabel (IM n))
                (projT2 (l item0)) e;
         input := input item0;
         destination := destination item0 j;
         output := output item0 |})
        (list_annotate from_projection
           (filter
              (fun a : vtransition_item X =>
               bool_decide (from_projection a))
              trx) Hall)) n2) = 
Some s2
exists (nX2 : nat) (sX1 sX2 : vstate X),
  0 <= nX2 /\
  sX1 j = sx j /\
  sX2 j = s2 /\
  nth_error (sx :: List.map destination trx) 0 =
  Some sX1 /\
  nth_error (sx :: List.map destination trx) nX2 =
  Some sX2

Hle:S n1 <= 0
Hs1:nth_error
  (sj
   :: List.map destination
        (finite_trace_projection_list_alt trx
           Hall)) (S n1) = 
Some s1
Hs2:nth_error
  (sj
   :: List.map destination
        (finite_trace_projection_list_alt trx
           Hall)) 0 = Some s2
exists (nX1 nX2 : nat) (sX1 sX2 : vstate X),
  nX1 <= nX2 /\
  sX1 j = s1 /\
  sX2 j = s2 /\
  nth_error (sx :: List.map destination trx) nX1 =
  Some sX1 /\
  nth_error (sx :: List.map destination trx) nX2 =
  Some sX2
 inversion Hle.

  (fun a : vtransition_item X =>
   bool_decide (from_projection a)) trx n2 =

Hn2th:nth_error trx nX2 = Some item2
nX1:nat
Hindex1:nth_error_filter_index
  (fun a : vtransition_item X =>
   bool_decide (from_projection a)) trx n1 =
Some nX1
Hn1th:nth_error trx nX1 = Some item1
exists (nX2 : nat) (sX1 sX2 : vstate X),
  S nX1 <= nX2 /\
  sX1 j = destination item1 j /\
  sX2 j = destination item2 j /\
  nth_error (sx :: List.map destination trx) (S nX1) =
  Some sX1 /\
  nth_error (sx :: List.map destination trx) nX2 =
  Some sX2

message, index:Type
IndEqDec:EqDecision index
IM:index -> VLSM message
i0:Inhabited index
constraint:composite_label IM ->
composite_state IM * option message ->
Prop

Xj:=composite_vlsm_constrained_projection IM
  constraint j:VLSM message
sx:state
trx:list transition_item
Htrx:finite_protocol_trace X sx trx
sj:state
Hsx:sx j = sj
Hall:Forall from_projection
  (filter
     (fun a : vtransition_item X =>
      bool_decide (from_projection a)) trx)
s1, s2:state
n1, n2:nat
Hle:n1 <= n2
Hs1:nth_error
  (sj
   :: List.map destination
        (finite_trace_projection_list_alt trx
           Hall)) n1 = 
Some s1
Hs2:nth_error
  (sj
   :: List.map destination
        (finite_trace_projection_list_alt trx
           Hall)) n2 = 
Some s2
HsX1:exists (nX1 nX2 : nat) 
(sX1 sX2 : vstate X),
  nX1 <= nX2 /\
  sX1 j = s1 /\
  sX2 j = s2 /\
  nth_error (sx :: List.map destination trx)
    nX1 = Some sX1 /\
  nth_error (sx :: List.map destination trx)
    nX2 = Some sX2
exists sX1 sX2 : vstate X,
  sX1 j = s1 /\ sX2 j = s2 /\ in_futures X sX1 sX2

Hproj:finite_trace_projection_list_alt trx Hall =
list_prefix lj n2
s1, s2:vstate (IM j)
Htrj:protocol_trace_prop Xj (Finite sj lj)
n1:nat
Hle:n1 <= n2
Hs1:trace_nth Xj
  (proj1_sig
     (exist
        (fun tr : Trace =>
         protocol_trace_prop Xj tr)
        (Finite sj lj) Htrj)) n1 = 
Some s1
Hs2:trace_nth Xj
  (proj1_sig
     (exist
        (fun tr : Trace =>
         protocol_trace_prop Xj tr)
        (Finite sj lj) Htrj)) n2 = 
Some s2
Heqtrj2:Finite sj (list_prefix lj n2) =
trace_prefix_fn Xj (Finite sj lj) n2
Hpref:protocol_trace_prop Xj
  (Finite sj (list_prefix lj n2))
Heq:finite_trace_projection_list_alt trx Hall =
finite_trace_projection_list trx
exists sX1 sX2 : vstate X,
  sX1 j = s1 /\ sX2 j = s2 /\ in_futures X sX1 sX2

  (proj1_sig

        (fun tr : Trace =>

IndEqDec:EqDecision index
IM:index -> VLSM message
i0:Inhabited index
constraint:composite_label IM ->
composite_state IM * option message ->
Prop
X:=composite_vlsm IM constraint:VLSM message
j:index
Xj:=composite_vlsm_constrained_projection IM
  constraint j:VLSM message
sj:state
lj:Stream transition_item
n2:nat
Hfr:exists
  (sx : vstate X) (trx : 
                   list 
                     (vtransition_item X)),
  finite_protocol_trace X sx trx /\
  sx j = sj /\
  finite_trace_projection_list trx =
  stream_prefix lj n2
s1, s2:vstate (IM j)
Htrj:protocol_trace_prop Xj (Infinite sj lj)
n1:nat
Hle:n1 <= n2
Hs1:trace_nth Xj
  (proj1_sig
     (exist
        (fun tr : Trace =>
         protocol_trace_prop Xj tr)
        (Infinite sj lj) Htrj)) n1 = 
Some s1
Hs2:trace_nth Xj
  (proj1_sig
     (exist
        (fun tr : Trace =>
         protocol_trace_prop Xj tr)
        (Infinite sj lj) Htrj)) n2 = 
Some s2
Heqtrj2:Finite sj (stream_prefix lj n2) =
trace_prefix_fn Xj (Infinite sj lj) n2
Hpref:protocol_trace_prop Xj
  (Finite sj (stream_prefix lj n2))
exists sX1 sX2 : vstate X,
  sX1 j = s1 /\ sX2 j = s2 /\ in_futures X sX1 sX2

  (Finite sj (stream_prefix lj n2))

        (stream_prefix lj n2)) n1

nth_error
  (sj :: List.map destination (stream_prefix lj n2))
  n2

  sX1 j = s1 /\ sX2 j = s2 /\ in_futures X sX1 sX2

    apply projection_friendly_in_futures' with sx trx sj Hall n1 n2; try assumption
    ; rewrite Hproj; rewrite <- Hs1 || rewrite <- Hs2; symmetry; assumption.
Qed.

End ProjectionTraces.

Section ProjectionTraces_membership.

Context
  {message : Type}
  {index : Type}
  {IndEqDec : EqDecision index}
  (IM : index -> VLSM message)
  {i0 : Inhabited index}
  (constraint : composite_label IM -> composite_state IM * option message -> Prop)
  (X := composite_vlsm IM constraint)
  .

j:=projT1 (l itemX):index
In
  {|
  l := projT2 (l itemX);
  input := input itemX;
  destination := destination itemX j;
  output := output itemX |}
  (finite_trace_projection_list IM constraint j tr)

message, index:Type
IndEqDec:EqDecision index
IM:index -> VLSM message
i0:Inhabited index
constraint:composite_label IM ->
composite_state IM * option message ->
Prop
X:=composite_vlsm IM constraint:VLSM message
a:vtransition_item X
tr:list (vtransition_item X)
itemX:vtransition_item X
HitemX:a = itemX
j:=projT1 (l itemX):index
IHtr:In itemX tr ->
In
  {|
  l := projT2 (l itemX);
  input := input itemX;
  destination := destination itemX j;
  output := output itemX |}
  (finite_trace_projection_list IM constraint j
     tr)
In
  {|
  l := projT2 (l itemX);
  input := input itemX;
  destination := destination itemX j;
  output := output itemX |}
  match decide (j = projT1 (l a)) with
  | left e =>
      {|
      l := eq_rect_r (fun n : index => vlabel (IM n))
             (projT2 (l a)) e;
      input := input a;
      destination := destination a j;
      output := output a |}
      :: finite_trace_projection_list IM constraint j
           tr
  | right _ =>
      finite_trace_projection_list IM constraint j tr
  end

      finite_trace_projection_list IM constraint
        (projT1 (l itemX)) tr
  end
